    FUW_PSSSHARIA_PSSPLUSPROSHARIA_PWMS_6: `6. The amount of contribution for <pru>PRU</pru.Well Medical Syariah may change in accordance with the Insured Participant's age, <i>Multiplier</i>, and <pru>PRU</pru> at the time of automatic renewal at each subsequent Policy Anniversary and may change at any time as an adjustment to, including but not limited to, Pengelola's overall claims experience, annual medical cost inflation, MY choice of <pru>PRU</pru> Saver with written notice in print, electronic or other form to ME no later than 30 (thirty) business days before the next nearest Policy Anniversary.`,
